            "type": "TEXT",
            "data": "\u003e\u003e Evaluando e integrando Análisis de Componentes Principales (PCA k\u003d2)...\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mpca\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.ml.feature.PCA\u001b[0m \u003d pca_d62f2ee36a72\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mdfPCA\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame\u001b[0m \u003d [IDENTIFICADOR: string, ANOMES: int ... 31 more fields]\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mextractPC1\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.expressions.UserDefinedFunction\u001b[0m \u003d SparkUserDefinedFunction($Lambda$5305/0x0000000841dcb840@6af19dee,DoubleType,List(Some(class[value[0]: vector])),Some(class[value[0]: double]),None,false,true)\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mextractPC2\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.expressions.UserDefinedFunction\u001b[0m \u003d SparkUserDefinedFunction($Lambda$5306/0x0000000841dcc840@114534ff,DoubleType,List(Some(class[value[0]: vector])),Some(class[value[0]: double]),None,false,true)\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mplotScatterPCA\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame\u001b[0m \u003d [PC1: double...\n"
